@@CreateSpellChecker
<TITLE CreateSpellChecker variable>
Summary
  Creates and returns an IJvSpellChecker instance if assigned.
Description
  Call CreateSpellChecker to create an IJvSpellChecker instance. Spell checkers that implements the
  IJvSpellChecker, assign their own function to this pointer. If the pointer is nil, no
  IJvSpellChecker implementor is registered.

  Since this function is actually a pointer, you shoud first check if it is nil before using it, i.e
  use a call like if Assigned(CreateSpellChecker).

