@@IJvSpellChecker.Seek
Summary
  Moves to another position in the text.
Description
  Seek moves the internal text pointer to the position in Text given by Position. If Position >=
  Length(Text), calls to Next always returns false.
Note
  Since positioning is 1-based, Seek(0) = Seek(1).
Parameters
  Position - The 1-based index to move the internal pointer to. Values < 1 are interpreted as 1,
  values >= Length(Text) are interpreted as Length(Text) - 1.
See Also
  IJvSpellChecker.Next, IJvSpellChecker.Text

